## Compliance Non-Negotiables

- NJ BROKERAGE LAW: Do not charge transaction-tied fees without legal
  clearance. Featured listing badge is safe. Everything else needs counsel.
- TCPA: Store explicit per-user per-channel per-sender consent before any
  automated texts. Not a blanket checkbox.
- FCRA: Do not build portable application with screening until a
  FCRA-compliant vendor (Checkr, TransUnion SmartMove) is signed AND NJ
  legal structure is resolved.
- FERPA: Students self-upload enrollment proof. Never receive student records
  directly from university.
- PCI: Use Stripe Checkout hosted page for all payments. Never let card
  numbers touch HouseRush servers.
- FAIR HOUSING: Listing linter must run before every listing goes live.

